    <item>
      <title>俄铝担心新的俄罗斯金属制裁将导致 36% 的销售额面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/rusal-fears-new-russia-metal-sanctions-put-36-of-sales-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯铝业巨头 United Co Rusal International PJSC 担心，由于英国和美国实施的制裁，其多达 36% 的销售额可能面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/rusal-fears-new-russia-metal-sanctions-put-36-of-sales-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟在玩弄多年后对中国发起贸易攻势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/eu-goes-on-china-trade-offensive-after-getting-played-for-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩正在对中国实施一系列贸易限制，她试图兑现让欧盟在全球舞台上成为更重要的政治参与者的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/eu-goes-on-china-trade-offensive-after-getting-played-for-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:47:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国、日本、韩国财务主管将在安全推动方面会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/us-japan-south-korea-finance-chiefs-to-meet-amid-security-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国、日本和韩国将于周三在华盛顿举行首次金融首脑会议，这是这三个盟国协调努力应对地缘政治和经济安全威胁的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/us-japan-south-korea-finance-chiefs-to-meet-amid-security-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国开始为最强大的模型起草人工智能法规</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/uk-starts-drafting-ai-regulations-for-most-powerful-models</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，英国正在开始起草管理人工智能的法规，重点关注支撑 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 的最强大的语言模型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/uk-starts-drafting-ai-regulations-for-most-powerful-models</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:49:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
